as about eight year old, ten year old when her mother died, near as I can tell you. And she got her - five brothers under her to look after, to pick 'em up you know. She had to take the load over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Then she had a big family herself?
