Well we had to look after ourselves, we had to do so many jobs and we had to do 'em. If they weren't done we got no food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 What sort of jobs did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Oh well I h
ad - I had a laundry - that laundry, had to go and fetch all the laundry in and bring it back, you know, to and from, two days a week, like two evenings. And Saturday, all day Saturday, just to take 'em away, and - take bundles of wood to the Co-op, I use
d
 to - take the barrow to fetch the wood in the morning, take a load of wood, or about twenty bundles, thirty bundles, as much as I could push, about two hundred yards from home and - come from school, dinnertime, they get all the wood tied on - much as I 
could - I could pull, bring it back home. When I got - had me dinner, I got to load me barrow up again and take that back to the Co-op - for the next journey. Two journeys each way each day.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 And you fitted school in between?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Oh you - I had to do
 it. Oh if there was anything missing - if I had - I had to get me wood - nails out the wood, and lay everything all in complete lengths and if I got time to mark each timber off where it got to be cut.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 What was the Co-op using it for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Well sell it firewood. Some in - well bundles of firewood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 What did you get paid for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 
Oh no, we never - mother - father did. Got - got it in groceries. Yes, you know, took it over in groceries. Yes, they came - paid in cash and he had it in grocerie
s. That's when the Co-op paid the - half a crown on a pound. That was a lot of money, 'cos a pound was a lot of money then to earn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Do you remember liking the job or didn't you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 We had to like it. We had to do - we had to do - if we - we
 didn't have to answer back. If we did we was down there. One clout back of your ear. Yes. No mucking about, you got on with it. You know what you got to do, get on with it. You was happier.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 How many rooms were there in the house at Berry Park?
