Well - anybody come in - anybody what - bring us some clothes and that. See - such as {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Tubby Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Cromwell Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, big people lived in there, Lansdowne well we used to go round odd jobs begging then. Well - that's the truth, begging.
 And - tap at the door and - go on boy, up the passage, out the way, hop it. And - they was in the front room. That's as far as we know. Next day or two I've got a another pair of trousers, bit out the knee and all that.
