All depends what time you got up, you had to be up a certain time else you wouldn't have got no breakfast. Oh yes, you got to be out the house and
 do so much work, get so much done before you go to school and you got to be at school at quarter to nine, and if you're late you'll get a - I know if you're late. See, you've got to do so much - and get there - by a certain time. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 What did you have for breakfast if you got any?
