 round, and she went to Hitchin hospital in a farm cart - oh about twelve, fourteen mile from Mepperhall to Hitchin, had it cut and turned, she was there some months, in the hospital. Had it cut and turned. And she was - hopping along. Not with a crutch b
ut with a stick. You know.
