Campton, that's fourteen or fifteen mile, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Sheffield{\*\xmlclose}
 that is, fourteen or fifteen mile from here and Berkhamstead, on the same thing. And that - we got about - dad done that 'cos he - looked after the horses and - it cost him very near nothing. Well them days it was near nothing, to what it is today.

