 No. He - when he was single I - heard - understood he had a drop or two and - they was married when they were seventeen, somewhere about seventeen, eighteen, mum and dad was. And - no - no beer, he hadn't got no taste for beer. I haven't. But my son, he 
likes a pint. Oh yes. Yes.
