{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Saxon Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 we had a big back garden, dad wanted it for - for allotment, you know for the - for the vegetables plants. Well I asked me uncles to make me a rabbit shed, you know, to put some r
abbits, 'cos that's what we lived on years ago, rabbits and fowls, when we could get them. Fowls. Yes. And rabbits. We had plenty of rabbits and - 'course dad, he - he had he took over two lots of allotments then, and that's where I had to go. When I left
 
work at night, I left at six, I got to be there be half past, walk there - do an; hour and a half's gardening or an hours' gardening which he knows how much I've got to do, I've got - do it a certain way and - then go home, he said, you're tea'll be waiti
ng for you.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Did you make more friends after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Well I had me friends, most friends were school pals you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Did you have girlfriends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 
Never troubled about 'em. Well I'd got - got me sisters, they - I - they were my biggest worry, sisters. Had so many of 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Did you still go on going to church and chapel just the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 
Well not so much as I - you know, I was made to go, that was only time as I went, when I was made to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 But you went less after you started work?
