We all walk - had to walk. I always had to walk in front so they could watch where I was going. I had to do it. They had to do these things. The older one of the family looked after the youngest one, and if you don't do it, I'll tell dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 What did you think of school?
