Oh well we had to put up with it dear, that's all you can say about it, we had to put up with it. We didn't think much of it, but - the teachers gradually see how thin
gs were and heard things and they come - put their arm round the back and, come on. I'll show you how to hold that - hold that pen. I'll show you how to hold that pencil.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 They were nice to you?
