No, not to my knowledge. No, they - we - never had all that. Not all that. We had a - now and again they had a - you know, little word with one another but - we never saw. We weren't allowed to see I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Did they encourage you at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10055362 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 
The teachers did but the parents, we - just get off to school, go on. They'll teach you what you've got to do, they'll tell you what you got to do. You 
understand what they say, you got to do as they tell you. And if you don't do it, we'll make you. So - you got to do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Did the other children come from the same sort of background as you?
