No, they didn't worry 'cos - I - had to - I had so much to do and I was told - anybody swore at you ignore it, come away, run away quick, come away from 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 Do you remember teachers having favourites?
