Well it seem they did but - somehow it looked they got a little bit higher than you were, put it that way you know - if you're in 
the shop or - they lived next to a shop you know - the child had - the teacher asked the child to call at the shop on the way back and all that. Well, they were a little favourite in there. Or you find out they've been putting the books out for a week or 
two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 That was a favourite jobs was it?
