That's - oh yes, oh yes. But once you find you're stopping in the class behind you know there's something wrong. - As you start get up go out, you, you, you - your names are called out, stop behind.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16147787 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8718839\charrsid1444406 How old were you when you left school?
